location.fullValue: Brookfield Plan, Wright's Landing at Legacy Park

data.description: Step into the embrace of this meticulously maintained residence, nestled in the heart of the highly coveted Legacy Park neighborhood.  Imagine yourself walking out of your fenced-in yard directly to a park and the walking / jogging path, which leads to a playground, brewery, coffee shop, community restaurants, karate studio, and shops in minutes. There is also a community clubhouse / fitness center just around the corner. So much to do without ever having to deal with traffic or crowds. Every weekend can feel like a retreat!  This home boasts over 2300 square feet of living space indoors, and a nicely sized fenced-in backyard with an extended patio for outdoor entertaining and leisure. Spend each day bathed in an abundance of natural light If you prefer less, just pull down the cordless privacy slatted blinds and enjoy your space. With added landscaping, interior and exterior features, and included appliances, this home surpasses the allure of new constructions. The first floor features a mud room, built-in bench and cubbies, and a powder room just off of the garage and foyer. To the right, you will find a more formal living room the current owners have been using as a playroom. The open-concept family room is next, with a gorgeous stone fireplace. Imagine reading books while sipping wine or hot chocolate, playing some games, or watching a movie. Open to the kitchen, you can utilize the large island for entertaining. There is no need to buy appliances, the matching matte-finished GE appliances all stay! The sink built into the island with disposal and LVP flooring help to make clean-up a breeze! So, entertain away!! The second floor boasts a large owner's suite with two walk-in closets, one of which boasts a window and has been transformed into a home office space. This fantastic sanctuary fits nicely alongside the three other impressively sized bedrooms. The second-floor laundry room cuts down on laundry time with a high efficiency washer and dryer that will stay with the home.  The basement, providing considerable space, also offers additional storage in the crawl space, an active radon system integrated into the foundation, a sump pit, and a visually appealing wet-look sealer on the floor. For electric car enthusiasts, an electrician has installed a high-speed EV charging outlet in the garage, which also features an extra-deep design and app-controlled door. There's so much to explore in this exceptional home. Don't miss out—schedule your showing today to experience the epitome of refined living.
